#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/reduce.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.reduce"
msgstr "# triton.language.reduce"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/reduce.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/reduce.md:4
msgid "简介：`triton.language.reduce` 沿指定轴 `axis` 对输入 tensor 应用 `combine_fn` 进行规约，返回规约后的结果张量。"
msgstr "Introduction: `triton.language.reduce` applies `combine_fn` along the specified axis `axis` to perform reduction on the input tensor, returning the reduced result tensor."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/reduce.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.reduce(input, axis, combine_fn, keep_dims=False, _semantic=None, _generator=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/reduce.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/reduce.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/reduce.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` 或 `tuple of Tensor` | 输入tensor，可以是单个tensor或tensor元组 |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` 或 `None` | 沿着哪个维度进行reduce操作。如果为None，则reduce所有维度 |\n"
"| `combine_fn` | `Callable` | 用于组合两个标量tensor组的函数（必须用@triton.jit标记） |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | 如果为True，保持被reduce的维度为长度1 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | `Optional[str]` | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
"| `_generator` | `Optional[Generator]` | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"|--------|------|------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` or `tuple of Tensor` | Input tensor, can be a single tensor or a tuple of tensors |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` or `None` | The dimension along which to perform the reduce operation. If None, all dimensions are reduced |\n"
"| `combine_fn` | `Callable` | Function used to combine two groups of scalar tensors (must be decorated with `@triton.jit`) |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | If True, keep the reduced dimensions with length 1 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | `Optional[str]` | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"
"| `_generator` | `Optional[Generator]` | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/reduce.md:14
msgid "**注意**：此函数也可以作为tensor的成员函数调用，如 `x.reduce(...)` 而不是 `reduce(x, ...)`"
msgstr "**Note**: This function can also be called as a member function of a tensor, such as `x.reduce(...)` instead of `reduce(x, ...)`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/reduce.md:16
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：沿指定轴 `axis` 规约后的结果张量。\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: The resulting tensor after reduction along the specified axis `axis`.\n"

